      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration lovers! This vehicle is looking for a dedicated new owner to bring back its former glory. While it's currently in poor condition and will require some mechanical and cosmetic attention, it serves as a fantastic, budget-friendly project for anyone who loves to roll up their sleeves. It's a rare chance to own this model at an incredibly accessible price and truly make it your own!",
