    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is an ideal choice for someone seeking reliable, budget-friendly transportation. While the engine is dependable and the car is fully drivable, potential buyers should expect visible signs of wear and tear, including some scratches on the exterior and minor staining on the upholstery. It has been maintained to keep it roadworthy, though it lacks the polish of a newer model. This is a solid, no-frills option for daily commuting.",
