    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently has a loud knocking sound and is leaking oil, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. The exterior shows heavy rust on the rocker panels and several large dents on the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and the air conditioning is non-functional. This would be an ideal project car or a source for parts, as it is not currently suitable for reliable daily use.",
